This folder contains code for the field computer to find the planes in each RGBD frame or each Mesh frame.
by Bhoram Lee 

Last Update: 2015. May. 20

Run main_stream_<Sensor Type>_<Task>.m (This is matlab code)
 

   ******************************
   If you want plots, 
   * [Sensor Type: lidar]set the second input argument of detectPlaneInstances_lidar function to a positive integer. 
   (in the 69th line). 
   example >> detectPlaneInstances_lidar_v5( ~ , 1 , ~); 

   * [Sensor Type: kinect] set  ui.figures(3) = 1;

   ****************************************
   Output
   * [Task: Door/Corner]: distance (meter), yaw (radian) 
   * [Task: Terrain]: TBD 


